  "title": "Accountant | Full Set | Diploma | Changi | 5.5 Days | Up To $5K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accountant</strong><br />Salary : $4200 - $5000<br />Working Days: Monday - Friday 8:30am to 5:30pm | Saturday 8:30am to 12:30 pm <br />Working Location: Changi South</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities </strong></p><ul><li>Handle full set of accounts independently, including AR, AP, GL, bank reconciliation and month end closing.</li><li>Make payroll and submit CPF monthly with HR system.</li><li>Update and follow up GIRO payment from different portals</li><li>Follow up with operation teams for monthly AR/AP closing</li><li>Prepare monthly management accounts, financial statements and schedules</li><li>Record and manage hire purchase and leasing transactions, including:  Capitalization of leased assets. Allocation of principal and interest , Monthly HP/Lease schedules and reconciliations &  Interest expense and liability tracking.</li><li>Prepare GST returns, ensure accuracy of GST treatment for HP and leasing transactions</li><li>Liaise with accounting firm for financial year statement, ECI</li><li>Maintain proper documentation and accounting records</li><li>Support year end closing and ad-hoc finance tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Accounting or equivalent</li><li>With full set accounting experience</li><li>Relevant working experience in freight forwarding industry is an advantage</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
